{"word":"G3343 - μεταπέμπω - metapémpō - met-ap-emp'-o - Call for","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μεταπέμπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">metapémpō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">met-ap-emp'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Call for</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழை"},{"paragraph":"1. to send one after"},{"paragraph":"2. sent for"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3326 - μετά - metá - met-ah'/3326\">G3326</a> and <a href=\"#/G3992 - πέμπω - pémpō - pem'-po/3992\">G3992</a>; to <i>send</i> from <i>elsewhere</i>, that is, (middle voice) to <i>summon</i> or <i>invite:</i> - call (send) for.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}